DroidWars 5 is a realtime mix of shoot'em up and action-strategy,
where the 'virtual-life-actors' (droids)
do their job independent,
determined by their individual equipment and/or weaponry.

You can -not- control the droids yourself,
except in Solo gametype. More info below.

DroidWars5 can be played by 0 to 3 human players.


